data.description: This beautiful partial stone and siding front home is located in a great spot that allows for easy walking access to the Franconia Springfield Metro. It sits on a one-acre lot surrounded by tall oak trees, providing a country living feel. The house boasts 4 bedrooms, 3.5 baths, and a 1-car garage with a large driveway that can fit up to 3 cars. The laundry/mud room is conveniently located off the kitchen, which is equipped with stainless steel appliances and granite counters. Skylights and French doors leading to a huge oversized deck provide stunning views. The huge living/dining room combination with wood floors includes a wood fireplace with a brick hearth and a den/office off the living room. The lower level has a 4th bedroom with an 11x8 closet, a separate utility room, and a storage room. The house also has newer windows which add to its appeal.  5 Min walk right out of your Backyard to access Rd that leads to Franconia Springfield METRO/ Buses (BLUE Line 25 mins to Pentagon)- Approx 1 Mile to FT Belvoir, 9  Miles to Pentagon (20 min drive). Terrific Schools Lane Elementary, Hayfield Middle/ High School.  See School Boundary Report in Documents-2 mi to I-395 (Mixing Bowl)-5 minutes BELTWAY ACCESS to D.C. Installations; Pentagon, FT McNair, Navy Yard, Quantico, FT Myer, Capitol Hill, Coast Guard Hqs, Bolling & Andrews AFB, GSA, DNI, CIA, DIA.  5 Minutes to Springfield Mall & Kingstowne Shopping Centers.
